<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Strict//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-strict.dtd">
<html lang="en" xml:lang="en" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
  <head>
    <title>Mixtress - The best mixes and live sets</title>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" content="text/html" http-equiv="Content-Type" />
    <link href="/favicon.ico" rel="shortcut icon" type="image/x-icon" />
    <link href="/favicon.ico" rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" />
    <meta content="Listen to the hottest long mixes from Soundcloud" name="description" />
    <link href="/stylesheets/styles.css" media="screen" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="info">
      <span class="about">About</span> |
      <span class="contact">Contact</span>
    </div>
    <div id="header">
      <a href="/" alt="mixtress: the best long mixes from soundcloud">
        <span class="welcome">welcome to...</span>
        <h1>Mixtress</h1>
      </a>
    </div>
    <div id="nav">
      <ul class="genres">
        <% @genres.each_with_index do |g, i| %>
          <li data-genre="<%= g %>" class="<%= 'first' if i.zero? %>"><%= g.capitalize %></li>
        <% end %>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div id="container"></div>

    <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.7.2/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="/scripts/soundcloud.api.js"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript">
      var _gaq = _gaq || [];
      _gaq.push(['_setAccount', 'UA-33565901-1']);
      _gaq.push(['_trackPageview']);

      (function() {
      // Only load the tracker if we aren't on localhost
      if(document.location.host.indexOf('localhost') < 0) {
        var ga = document.createElement('script'); ga.type = 'text/javascript'; ga.async = true;
        ga.src = ('https:' == document.location.protocol ? 'https://ssl' : 'http://www') + '.google-analytics.com/ga.js';
        var s = document.getElementsByTagName('script')[0]; s.parentNode.insertBefore(ga, s);
      }
      })();
    </script>
    <script src="/scripts/mixtress.js?v=3"></script>
    <script src="/scripts/jquery.simplemodal.js"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript">
      $(function() {
        $('#info span.about').click(function() { $('#about').modal(); });
        $('#info span.contact').click(function() { $('#contact').modal(); });
      });
    </script>

    <div id="about" style="display: none">
      <h2>About</h2>
      <div>
        Everybody's got a favorite band, a favorite album, a favorite song.  You've invested into it your time, and from that investment spawned an intimate relationship. You're familiar with every texture and tone — that snare rush three minutes into the track still gives you goosebumps.
      </div>
      <div>
        But it's been a while.  It seems played.  Waking up one morning, you're surprised to find that, like a butterfly emerging from its cocoon, you can see the world outside.  The romance is over and you know it — here's your Mixtress.
      </div>
    </div>

    <div id="contact" style="display: none">
      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <form action="/contact" method="post">
        <label for="name">Name:</label>
        <input type="text" name="name">
        <label for="email">Email:</label>
        <input type="text" name="email">
        <label for="to">Message:</label>
        <textarea name="message" rows="10" cols="80"></textarea>
        <input type="submit" value="Send the Love">
      </form>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
